OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain developing into the evening as a
OL,7,Fband of rain moves southeastwards
OL,8,Facross the region. Becoming mostly dry
OL,9,Flater in the night, although risk of
OL,10,Fan isolated shower, with perhaps a few
OL,11,Fclear spells developing towards dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FAfter a cool start, it will
OL,14,Fbe a dry day, with variable amounts of
OL,15,Fcloud and some bright or sunny spells.
OL,16,FFeeling cooler compared to previous
OL,17,Fdays. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
